This paper involves optimization problems related to facility location and transportation, which are common topics in computer science. The use of highways and the consideration of different types of highways suggest that this paper may belong to the sub-categories of computational geometry (cs.CG) or algorithms (cs.DS). The problem formulation and the use of optimization techniques suggest that this paper may also belong to the sub-categories of game theory (cs.GT), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), or machine learning (cs.LG).
